ClassDesc: Used to notify callers of @B_android#telephony#TelephonyManager#sendUssdRequest_E@ when the network either successfully executes a USSD request, or if there was a failure while executing the request. @B_android#telephony#TelephonyManager#UssdResponseCallback#onReceiveUssdResponse_E@ will be called if the USSD request has succeeded. @B_android#telephony#TelephonyManager#UssdResponseCallback#onReceiveUssdResponseFailed_E@ will be called if the USSD request has failed.
